        <p>
        The <a href="https://github.com/lelylan/device-component-ng">Device Component</a>
        is an HTML5 tag we use to represent a device on a web page. If you are a frontend
        developer play with it's code and create new device specific components for lights,
        locks, thermostats and more.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="right small">
        <%= image_tag 'developers/designers.png' %>
      </div>
      <div class="clearfix"></div>
    <hr/>
    </div>

