      <div class="left small">
        <%= image_tag 'developers/simulation.png' %>
      </div>
      <div class="right big">
        <h2>Simulation first</h2>
        <p>
        With Lelylan you do not need any physical hardware to get started. Every device,
        when not connected to the physical world, simulates its behaviour. This means
        you can start building your apps without any initial cost.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="clearfix"></div>
    <hr/>
    </div>

    <div class="inner row">
      <div class="left big">
        <h2>Techs</h2>
        <p>
        Lelylan uses as core techs Ruby and Node.js for the backend and AngularJS for the frontend.
        We also support Realtime Notifications, OAuth2 Authorizations and the CORS specs to allow
        cross-domain communication from the browser.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="right small">
        <%= image_tag 'developers/techs.png' %>
      </div>
      <div class="clearfix"></div>
    <hr/>
    </div>

